INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('125', '公司简介', 'Company profile', '1536202850', '67', '<p>\r\n	深圳洋星通运国际货运代理有限公司，英文简称A&amp;E，位于中国经济特区深圳，是集海运、空运、陆运为一体的现代国际物流企业，为客户量身定制并保障执行简洁高效、风险可控的货物运输一站式解决方案，是国家一级货运代理资质（无船承运资格证书：NVOCC-02442），是世界货运代理联盟（WCA）成员、中国国际物流网（CGLN）理事单位、深圳市货代协会副会长单位。主营国际海运、国际空运、陆运、门到门的多式联运，特种货物、拖车，清关，货物质检，货物保险，仓储与分流，产品原产证和签发货贷单、DDU、DDP等业务。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	作为深圳领先的货代物流企业，洋星自2000年成立来一直致力于推动货代业国际化进程，整合优势资源不断开辟新的航运渠道，现已在广州、上海、宁波、青岛、澳大利亚悉尼多个主要港口城市设立分公司，并与WANHAI、OOCL、COSCO、APL、YML、MSK、MOL、HPLY等世界各大船公司保持密切稳定的合作关系，成功搭建以深圳、悉尼为双枢纽，辐射全球的国际运输网络，在中东、印巴、东南亚、澳洲等航线上保持了强大竞争力的价格优势、服务优势、货量优势，服务遍布各行业多领域，成为众多著名产品国际间贸易的合作者和运输专家，深受行业内外的高度评价。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	洋星是一个大家庭，员工是公司的宝贵财富和中流砥柱，培养员工的创新意识和服务意识，大力倡导温馨、友爱、互助、上进的人文环境，提升员工的幸福感和企业凝聚力，丰富多彩的各项主题活动和社会慈善行动都让员工们赋予了责任感和担当力，成为行业里的优秀人才。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	多年来，洋星坚持全球化视野，在世界经济一体化背景下，全面实施“创新+服务”理念，大力开发电子商务平台，着力打造一体化物流解决方案，不断铸造高品质服务体验，为客户的成功提供了坚实有力的支持与保障，未来，洋星将持续发力，整合全球优质物流运输资源，满足国内外客户更多个性化需求，探索全球化货代新的模式，把洋星发展成为具有行业价值、社会价值的有责任感的现代化国际化的物流企业。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/public/upload\\kind\\20180906/4f833bf75a78151e1a5a1faddc3eef6f.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>', null, '0', '0', '', '0', '1535904000', '', 'Shenzhen Yang Xing Tong International Freight Forwarder Co., Ltd, located in Shenzhen, China\'s Special Economic Zone, is a modern international logistics enterprise which integrates ocean, air and land transportation. It is a one-stop solution for customer-tailored and guaranteed to implement concise, efficient and risk-controllable freight transportation. It is a first-class freight forwarder in China. NVOCC-02442 is a member of WCA, a member of China International Logistics Network (CGLN) and vice-chairman of Shenzhen Freight Forwarders Association. Mainly engaged in international shipping, international air transport, land transport, door-to-door multimodal transport, special goods, trailers, customs clearance, cargo quality inspection, cargo insurance, warehousing and diversion, product certificate of origin and the issuance of credit, DDU, DDP and other business.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs a leading freight forwarding logistics enterprise in Shenzhen, Yangxing has been committed to promoting the internationalization of freight forwarding industry since its establishment in 2000, integrating its superior resources and constantly opening up new shipping channels. Now it has set up branches in several major port cities in Guangzhou, Shanghai, Ningbo, Qingdao, Australia and Sydney, and has established branches with WANHAI, OOCL, COSCO. APL, YML, MSK, MOL, HPLY and other major shipping companies in the world have maintained close and stable cooperative relations. They have successfully established an international transport network with Shenzhen and Sydney as two hubs, radiating the whole world. They have maintained a strong competitive price advantage, service advantage and cargo volume advantage in the Middle East, India-Pakistan, Southeast Asia, Australia and other routes. It has been widely used in various industries and fields, and has become a collaborator and transportation expert in international trade of many famous products. It has been highly appraised both inside and outside the industry.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOcean Star is a big family. Employees are the company\'s valuable wealth and mainstay. They cultivate their sense of innovation and service, advocate a warm, friendly, cooperative and progressive humanistic environment, enhance their sense of happiness and corporate cohesion, and enrich their various thematic activities and social charity activities. It has given a sense of responsibility and responsibility to become an excellent talent in the industry.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	Over the years, Yang Xing has adhered to the vision of globalization, fully implemented the concept of \"innovation + service\" in the context of world economic integration, vigorously developed e-commerce platforms, strived to create integrated logistics solutions, and constantly forged high-quality service experience, providing solid and powerful support and protection for the success of customers in the future. Star will continue to make efforts to integrate global high-quality logistics and transportation resources, meet more individual needs of customers at home and abroad, explore new models of global freight forwarding, and develop Star into a modern and international logistics enterprise with industry value and social value.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/public/upload\\kind\\20180906/be78e73dcc635d19026a0a2b52251aba.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>');
