experience, providing solid and powerful support and protection for the success of customers in the future. Star will continue to make efforts to integrate global high-quality logistics and transportation resources, meet more individual needs of customers at home and abroad, explore new models of global freight forwarding, and develop Star into a modern and international logistics enterprise with industry value and social value.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/public/upload\\kind\\20180906/be78e73dcc635d19026a0a2b52251aba.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</p>');
