INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('134', '国际海运服务', 'International Maritime Service', '1536203443', '96', '<p>\r\n	商业货物的国际运输是一个价值数十亿美元的行业，其中包含了大部分国际货运。商业货物是指除活体动物和个人物品/家庭用品外的所有货物。PCF拥有知识，网络和安全技能，可以在国内提取货物，安排运送到我们的仓库或其他地点，并处理海外货物的国际运输。我们为商业货物提供海运，空运，卡车和铁路服务。你需要门到门服务吗？我们可以通过我们的全球代理商网络处理门到门服务。在提供报价之前，我们将与您坐下来确定您的项目范围。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src=\"/public/upload\\kind\\20180906/72335692853124c7391e32efee99f562.jpg\" alt=\"\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	我们提供海运（海运）货运整合和全集装箱运输<br />\r\n-LCL（小于集装箱装载）运输包括来自您或您供应商的内陆运输 - <br />\r\n买家的合并：我们可以在我们的仓库网络中整合货物，直到您有足够的货物填充自己的容器<br />\r\n-FCL（满载集装箱）运输：我们提供门到门多式联运服务。我们可以将集装箱运送到您或您的供应商的设施进行装载\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	我们拥有各种类型的商业货物的经验，包括但不限于： <br />\r\n- 建筑设备 <br />\r\n- 机械<br />\r\n- 汽车零部件<br />\r\n- 展览材料<br />\r\n- 运动休闲设备<br />\r\n- 石油和天然气设备 <br />\r\n-零售产品（例如食品/饮料，化妆品，家用产品等快速消费品）<br />\r\n- Flexi-Tanks和ISO-Tanks <br />\r\n- 其他商业设备（如厨房设备，家具，瓷砖，管道等）<br />\r\n无论货物是否有危险，大或小，重或轻，在L / C（信件）信誉）或不，我们有经验和客户服务来处理您的货物。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	专业处理知识<br />\r\n每种类型的货物都需要了解该货物以供美国海关使用，清关，处理，装载和运输。有以下要求：<br />\r\n是否有危险？需要什么类型的美国海关或工业和安全局清关？如何打包？如何加载？买什么类型的保险？如何在目的地处理？\r\n</p>', '/public/upload/article/20181019/df9b9d283f2cc71525a2c925cb2f370c.png', '0', '1', '我们提供完整的供应链管理包，包括具有成本效益和快速海运。您也可以将此套餐与其他交通方式结合使用。', '0', '1535904000', 'We provide a complete supply chain management package, including cost-effective and fast shipping. You can also combine this package with other modes of transportation.', 'The international transport of commercial goods is a multibillion-dollar industry that includes most of the international freight. Commercial goods refer to all goods except live animals and personal belongings. PCF has the knowledge, network and security skills to pick up goods at home, arrange shipments to our warehouses or other locations, and handle international shipments of goods overseas. We provide shipping, air freight, truck and rail services for commercial goods. Do you need door to door service? We can handle door to door services through our global agent network. Before offering the quotation, we will sit down with you to confirm your project scope.<br />\r\n<img src=\"/public/upload\\kind\\20180906/76ffb16a85f985f6bce05502ecab5241.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe provide marine (SEA) freight consolidation and full container transportation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-LCL (less than container loading) transportation includes inland transportation from you or your supplier.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBuyer merger: We can integrate goods in our warehouse network until you have enough to fill your container<br />\r\n<br />\r\n-FCL (full loaded container) transportation: we provide door-to-door multimodal services. We can ship containers to your or your supplier\'s facilities for loading.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe have experience in various types of commercial goods, including but not limited to:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- building equipment.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Machinery<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCar parts<br />\r\n<br />\r\nExhibition materials<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSports leisure equipment<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- oil and natural gas equipment<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- retail products (such as fast food products, beverages, cosmetics, household products, etc.)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n- Flexi-Tanks and ISO-Tanks<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* other commercial facilities (such as kitchen equipment, furniture, tiles, pipes, etc.)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhether the goods are dangerous, large or small, heavy or light, in L/C (letter) reputation) or not, we have experience and customer service to handle your goods.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nProfessional knowledge<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach type of cargo needs to be known for use, clearance, handling, loading and transportation by the U.S. Customs. There are the following requirements:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIs there any danger? What type of customs clearance or industrial and safety administration is required? How to pack? How to load? What kind of insurance do you buy? How to deal with the destination?');
